::DarkMouse::

She looked around and couldn't find a way in on the ground side.  She 
looked up and saw a vent high up the side of the ship.  She decided 
another tackic to gain access into the ship would be nessassary.

She walked around to the side of the ship where there was another 
doorway.  She saw someone standing there whom she didn't know.  She 
walked up with her hands up over her head.
 
"I wish to talk to your leader about joining you."

She knew that if they had Quickstrike, he would be in the brig.  They 
would put her in the brig as well.  Once joined again with 
Quickstrike, they could break out together.
